{"tid":2400584,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"加拿大「青年人才」工作簽證今起可申請 須18歲以上無年齡上限（附懶人包）","createTime":"2021-02-09T05:24:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T07:57:41.000Z","uid":48083,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"94558fc7135bddef3090cc9ec04f867da7de43e7","tid":2400584,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:24:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210209/2GEOCWENXFHLRBPH6VSKPRK6QQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210209%2F2GEOCWENXFHLRBPH6VSKPRK6QQ%2F&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMCWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=577a0430\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210209%2F2GEOCWENXFHLRBPH6VSKPRK6QQ%2F&h=692b1d5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210209/2GEOCWENXFHLRBPH6VSKPRK6QQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n北京自行為港訂立《國安法》，國際社會紛斥令香港法治倒退，持續向香港提供支援。加拿大去年便因應香港實施《國安法》，宣佈為港人提供「救生艇計劃」協助香港抗爭者，其中針對「青年人才」的工作簽證政策今日起正式接受申請（詳情可參閱相關資料網站），亦提供更多細節，包括申請人須為年滿18歲或以上，但不設年齡上限，而有關計劃有兩年申請期，至2023年2月7日結束。<br />\n<br />\n根據計劃，凡持有香港特別行政區或BNO護照、最近5年內完成當地大專課程或持外國相等學歷的大專畢業生，今日起可透過申請為期3年的工作簽證，移居加國。一直推動有關計劃的人權組織「Hong Kong Watch（香港監察）」指，有關計劃要求申請人需年滿18歲或以上，但不設年齡上限。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原source <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/corporate/mandate/policies-operational-instructions-agreements/public-policies/hong-kong-residents-open-work-permit.html?fbclid=IwAR3Ph9RO76p8p4yNdHsVi_4vvoDuL9rGCdLs2vs09JgoRa7NYB62IN4DlLw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.canada.ca%2Fen%2Fimmigration-refugees-citizenship%2Fcorporate%2Fmandate%2Fpolicies-operational-instructions-agreements%2Fpublic-policies%2Fhong-kong-residents-open-work-permit.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3Ph9RO76p8p4yNdHsVi_4vvoDuL9rGCdLs2vs09JgoRa7NYB62IN4DlLw&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMCWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=ffe1a503\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.canada.ca/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/corporate/mandate/policies-operational-instructions-agreements/public-policies/hong-kong-residents-open-work-permit.html?fbclid=IwAR3Ph9RO76p8p4yNdHsVi_4vvoDuL9rGCdLs2vs09JgoRa7NYB62IN4DlLw</a>"},{"pid":"6c482471cb6cf18e8a327025be351901d9415d3b","tid":2400584,"uid":389613,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:24:51.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">不論離開定堅守都係手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span> </span><br />\n<br />\n決意堅守陣地既手足，必須時刻警惕提防，保留有用之軀，日後方能煲底相見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我認為<span class=\"red\">中共已撕破臉皮，唔會再講法理情，更盡一切辦法會趕盡殺絕</span>，本土戰線只餘硬碰硬一著，而港共武裝與抗爭者實力相距太大，難成氣候，除非把抗爭層面擴大化，將火魔、簡易組裝槍械等等變成家家戶戶都有的必備品，否則難以對抗如同送頭，亦無必要，而且傳播該類資訊係十分頭痛既問題，能參與者的數量亦成疑。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"> 但  <span class=\"red\">今次 BNO 大量港人走資走人不旦只可以保有用之驅全身而退保存實力，更可以逼中共支爆發難，借東風引天下圍中，百國聯軍，打柒老共，核平北京！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>所以：</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><ins><span class=\"xx-large\"> <span class=\"red\">離開唔係逃避，係主動攬炒救香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></ins></em></strong><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>警號已經響起咗！<span class=\"red\">越著時間過去，離開香港將會日漸困難</span>，大時代中不能存有饒幸之心，成日同自己講冇事既、冇事既個d人，就係走唔切，困咗係東德既人。<span class=\"red\">總之任何人，有得即走，特別高風險人士一定要最早走，其他人遲極唔可以遲過外國撤僑，外國第一個國家撤僑你就要跟住飛。外國唔會一次過撤，會比時間同signal香港人走先。</span>切記你係難民唔係移民。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪好好奇美國點解得把口唔出手制裁？我話你知幾時先制裁、有冇可能封關、應唔應該走、幾時要走。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2093986\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2093986</a><br />\n<br />\n(分析)仲有幾耐入東突(新疆)模式，見到咩警告要流亡？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1980175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1980175</a><br />\n<br />\n香港簡易流亡手冊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/478029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/478029</a><br />\n<br />\n[借古鑑今] 中國因逃亡潮於 1951 年 2 月 15 日鎖關，香港因 BNO 鎖關的憂慮正響歐美之間蔓延！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2390806\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2390806</a>"},{"pid":"51564a918be555b71a32c8cf7a4f9e50d2469955","tid":2400584,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:25:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65936fee822c4dc718e230e14f702c00c5b2f2eb","tid":2400584,"uid":125017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:27:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>須18歲以上無年齡上限</blockquote><br />\nLM 又比人屌誤導"},{"pid":"00916ef138c993b8019bee57d6f11d24fc62a527","tid":2400584,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:27:58.000Z","msg":"又益支那人"},{"pid":"6703c9b68db8726018eec24471d567803eb14502","tid":2400584,"uid":307927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:28:18.000Z","msg":"做滿3年可以拎護照+入藉？"},{"pid":"4b449701621e33b8336cdb967ab9df8add311962","tid":2400584,"uid":287891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6703c9b68db8726018eec24471d567803eb14502","tid":2400584,"uid":307927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:28:18.000Z","msg":"做滿3年可以拎護照+入藉？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:29:10.000Z","msg":"做一年PR 再逗留三年入籍"},{"pid":"e1205dac2602a5a8e07c2c9edcefdb3b251a1b01","tid":2400584,"uid":253016,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:30:27.000Z","msg":"雙非港漂大量支那賤畜is very<br />\n<br />\n到時候簽證人口 支那豬:港人 10:1<br />\n支那拯救計劃 利害了我的加<br />\n遲早玩到排華 順便連班土著藍絲都玩殘埋"},{"pid":"9c190924fe1e52cdde3b9d0152d69f84cdc5fadd","tid":2400584,"uid":307927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4b449701621e33b8336cdb967ab9df8add311962","tid":2400584,"uid":287891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6703c9b68db8726018eec24471d567803eb14502","tid":2400584,"uid":307927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-0